from maridai subject traveling fatima wa re consecration and anniversary hello i just like to share thi rosary and other prayer propagation practice we do in my country i be not sure if it be go on also here in the u or any other country in all these yr i be here in illinoi usa i have not encounter it may i just call it traveling fatima since i do know of an exact translation of what we call it in my native language for certain region in a district in a town or city an image statue of my lady of fatima be move from one home originate from owner to another thi will stay with that family for one week and thi family be require to pray the rosary and other prayer prayer sheet accompany the image to my lady of fatima the move will be like a simple procession of folk pick up the image from it current after prayer and proceed to move it to the next home which ha the prior notification about the move there will be the prayer at the next home to welcome my lady of fatima image there it do not have to be that only member of the family in that home who must pray to the image they may invite other or can invite themself in to participate during prayer time in that home everyday for one week thi image be move from one family to the next within the bound region of that district until it go back to the owner of the image thi be probably go on around there philippine right now or somebody correct me when exactly since i forget and every year thi be part of my devotion to my lady of fatima it ha be easy to facilitate thi back home because it be more likely that ymy next door neighbor be a catholic and the image then be just move next door i be think of start something like it in the village where my sister and her family life most of my friend and neighbor there be catholic and practice one i like to know if there be any law that thi practice will violate whatsoever before i go for it thank you for any comment or help about thi matter marida maridai 